ygData.messageBody:
Hehe why everyone think new server crowded? When I login Prexus last night
at 10pm, it's again the server with least players. When I logout at 2am,
it's the 3rd server with least players ;)

The patch last night has increased monster spawning - I can see red
skeleton everywhere just outside Ak-Anon - you just need a full house team
and start go banging. I team with a warrior and killed a puma - 1/4 bubb
rise in xp ;)

As for Prexus branch division, no thx, hehe. UO guild is enuff for me.
Btw, tonight I'm meeting my local UO kakis, brainwashing them to try EQ @
Prexus. Since Prexus is a new server, they wont be too far away once they
start a new char there.

Mondain.
